message.content: cs.MM, cs.CV, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.MM (Multimedia, Computer Vision, Information Theory, Machine Learning, Multimedia) - The paper focuses on video compression and streaming, which falls under the domain of multimedia. The proposed method involves training a binary autoencoder, which is a machine learning technique, hence it can also be categorized under machine learning. The use of residual information and binary representations also suggests that the paper may fall under computer vision and information theory.
